'''Richard Allen Lupoff''' ([[21 February|February 21]], [[1935]] - [[22 October|October 22]], [[2020]])  was an American science fiction and mystery author, and an expert on [[wikipedia:Edgar Rice Burroughs|Edgar Rice Burroughs]] and [[wikipedia:H. P. Lovecraft|H. P. Lovecraft]].

In his [[1965]] book on Burroughs, ''[[Edgar Rice Burroughs: Master of Adventure]]'', Lupoff quoted from [[Letter to Richard Lupoff|a letter from J.R.R. Tolkien]].<ref>''An Illustrated Tolkien Bibliography'', at Tolkienbooks.net</ref>
